rows.label: tev056201_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire

rows.label: tev056201_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Bubu about his family.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056201_JNK0020
rows.name: Discuss

rows.label: tev056201_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Bubu if anything is troubling him.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056201_MSG0001
rows.name: Wife of Bubu is really cute, right? Lana just like angel![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056201_MSG0002
rows.name: So Bubu decided to move to city to keep angel safe.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056201_MSG0003
rows.name: Move was expensive, but Lana is priceless![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056201_MSG0004
rows.name:
Is friend BLADE? Bubu counting on friend to keep city
safe, okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056201_MSG0005
rows.name:
Just think about how privileged friend is to live in city
containing such lovely angel! That should be all the
inspiration friend needs.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056201_MSG0008
rows.name: Angel wife Lana often goes out alone at night.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056201_MSG0009
rows.name:
When Bubu asks about late-night wanderings,
Lana says she is learning how to be even more cute.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056201_MSG0010
rows.name:
Talk about reckless! If Lana get any more adorable,
head of Bubu might explode from cuteness overload![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056201_MSG0011
rows.name:
But anyway, it seem quite dangerous at night,
so Bubu asked servant Walolo to accompany Lana.
Walolo will die protecting Lana if need be![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056201_SEL1011
rows.name: Ask Bubu about the caravans.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056201_SEL1021
rows.name: Ask Bubu about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056201_MSG0012
rows.name: Running caravan is hard work.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056201_MSG0013
rows.name:
Bubu always let Walolo manage things,
so now that Walolo gone, Bubu struggling.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056201_MSG0014
rows.name:
Lana say Walolo ran away to destroy caravan of
Bubu. Meh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056201_MSG0015
rows.name:
That really mean way to repay kindness of Bubu!
Where would Walolo be without generous mentor?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056201_MSG0016
rows.name:
But no matter. Bubu still going to make caravan best
in whole wide world of Mira. Then stupid jaw of
Walolo will drop open like hinge![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056201_MSG0019
rows.name:
Bubu not understand... Why did Lana not apologize
to Bubu?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056201_MSG0020
rows.name: Bubu was so so so so SOOO worried about angel![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056201_MSG0021
rows.name: And yet... And yet...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056201_MSG0022
rows.name:
Bubu glad Lana come back, but Bubu not able to
have happy chats just yet.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056201_MSG0023
rows.name:
Until Lana learn lesson and apologize,
Lana will get angry, prickly husband! Meh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056201_SEL2011
rows.name: Ask Bubu about Walolo.

rows.label: tev056201_SEL2021
rows.name: Ask Bubu about recent developments.

rows.label: tev056201_MSG0024
rows.name: Gossip travels fast in Nopon community...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056201_MSG0025
rows.name:
Everyone know that Lana run off with Walolo.
Meeeeh...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056201_MSG0026
rows.name:
Of course, Nopon blame EVERYTHING on Bubu.
Say that Bubu is poor excuse for leader...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056201_MSG0027
rows.name:
But that not true! Walolo just got tricked by angelic
face of Lana. Her beauty cast wicked spell and made
Walolo act funny.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056201_MSG0028
rows.name:
All Walolo have to do is apologize and... Nope.
Never mind. Bubu not nice enough to forgive Walolo.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056201_MSG0031
rows.name:
Was Bubu supposed to make favorite foods of Lana
more often? Where did Bubu go wrong?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056201_MSG0032
rows.name:
Maybe Bubu should have put more thought into which
bodyguard to send out with angel wife...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056201_MSG0033
rows.name: Or maybe Bubu will never know. Meeeeeh...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056201_MSG0034
rows.name:
Bubu needs more time to think. Then Bubu decide
whether or not to go find Lana again.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056201_MSG0035
rows.name: If Lana even want to be found... *sniff*[ST:wait ]
